import React, { useEffect, useRef } from "react"; function Modal() { const modal = useRef(); useEffect(()=>{},[ modal.current.addEventListener("click", e => { const dialogDimensions = modal.current.getBoundingClientRect() if ( e.clientX < dialogDimensions.left || e.clientX > dialogDimensions.right || e.clientY < dialogDimensions.top || e.clientY > dialogDimensions.bottom ) { modal.current.close() } }) ]) return ( <>
); } export default Modal;
